ing: 1 (10.75 ounce) can  condensed cream of mushroom soup
des: "This is a recipe my mom always cooks when she doesn't have much time.  It only has three ingredients, but it tastes great!  This will surely be a family pleaser! Serve over rice or noodles. I even like it with a slice of bread."
ins:
In a large skillet over medium heat, cook the ground beef until evenly browned; drain.
Stir in condensed cream of mushroom soup and condensed vegetable soup. Cook for 10 to 15 minutes, stirring frequently, until gently boiling.
